					Trusted Expertise in Federal Program Management and Cost-Saving
					Solutions
				</h1>

				<p class='text-white text-lg max-[450px]:text-base'>
					KTC brings over 13 years of expertise in Program Management,
					Engineering, and Consulting Services, trusted by federal clients
					across defense and civilian sectors. With a proven track record
					of reducing costs and boosting efficiency, KTC delivers
					consistent, high-quality results tailored to meet client needs.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class='flex max-[550px]:flex-col gap-2'>
				<div>
					<a
						href='/'
						class='block font-medium max-[550px]:text-center text-white bg-leaf py-3 px-6'
						>Explore our Services</a
					>
