			</div>

			<div class='max-[1145px]:max-w-128'>
				<h2 class='font-bold text-leaf mb-3'>ABOUT KT CONSULTING</h2>

				<h3 class='text-2xl font-bold mb-4'>
					Your Trusted Partner for Excellence in Program Management and
